title: All ITTF Rankings
subtitle: In CSV and SQL database
description:
Internation Table Tennis Federation rankings for all of the following categories: Men's singles, Men's doubles, Women's singles, and Women's doubles. player_rank.db contains all of the -data.csv files, metadata.db contains all of the -metadata.csv files. 
 [Data source](https://www.ittf.com/rankings) 
 [Men's Singles Ranking Dashboard](https://ittf-autoscrape.onrender.com/) 
 [GitHub repo](https://github.com/kenf1/ITTF-Autoscrape)
